// E2E fixture: Supervisor that registers its Counter child under the
// name `#bt1991SupCounter` with a permanent restart policy. Used to
// verify that a name-resolving proxy (`Actor named:`) transparently
// survives supervised restarts (BT-1991 / ADR 0079).

Supervisor subclass: E2ENamedSupervisor

  class children -> List =>
    spec := Counter supervisionSpec withName: #bt1991SupCounter withRestart: #permanent
    #(spec)
